11→ * - Agents: {dir}/agents/{name}.json (JSON)
12→ * - MCP: {dir}/plugins/config.json → mcpServers key (nested JSON)
13→ * - Hooks: {dir}/settings.json → hooks key (event→handler map)
14→ */
